$ Excel: View -> Window -> Freeze Pane

*Freeze Pane* allows to keep a specified portion (such as first row or left most column) of a → Microsoft/Office/Excel/Object-Model/Worksheet visible while navigating through the rest of the worksheet.

In → development/languages/VBA, this functionality is exposed through → Microsoft/Office/Excel/Object-Model/Window#excel-window-freezePanes[`window.freezePanes`].
